{"title":"跨上火箭篇","authors":["郭沫若"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":9,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨上火箭篇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭沫若"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设遵循总路线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰轰烈烈活鲜鲜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化革命上骏马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"技术革命箭离弦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政治挂帅党领导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自力更生学苏联。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地大物博人口多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"超美超英有何难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见早稻三万六，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又传中稻四万三；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"繁昌不愧叫繁昌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧紧追赶麻城县。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不闻钢铁千万二，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再过几年一万万？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛郎织女无颜色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盘古女娲骇破胆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农生产大跃进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算盘无法再计算。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"需要电子计算机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家望着科学院。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文艺也有试验田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卫星几时飞上天？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农文章遍天下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作家何得再留连？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"科学技术待跟上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文艺也还掉得远。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坏事可能变好事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这儿有了对立面。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破除迷信争独创，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放思想走尖端。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揭下专家作家相，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老年变作青少年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农姿态来出现，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"参加劳动受锻炼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学得工农真本事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"产量就能翻几番。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不仅量多且质好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不仅透红且深专。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"基本粒子被冲破，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交响乐章入云端。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原子导弹造奇迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一直飞出九重天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热核风镐显神通，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把地球也凿穿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江三峡已发电，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电光照亮东海边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天山冰雪化为水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灌溉戈壁成良田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国都是运河网，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北自黑龙南海南。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汉水北流入黄河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄海已成一片蓝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自然风物有改变，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会文化更鲜妍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺风耳和千里眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有色电视在面前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处都是新李杜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处都有新屈原。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荷马但丁不稀罕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莎士比亚几万千。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李冰蔡伦接联翩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建筑圣人赛鲁班。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哥白尼同达尔文，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛顿居里肩并肩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血吸虫病成古典，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恶性肿瘤已游仙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人都是多面手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人口十亿还有尖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人多粮多棉纱多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化学工业满山川。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化学食品和纤维，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要吃要穿用不完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民内部有矛盾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随时展开大辩论。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢想敢说又敢作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矛盾促进大发展。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力争上游争上上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓足干劲没边缘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽多尽快尽好省，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天等于二十年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各尽所能取所需，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将成老生之常谈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人间天国乌托邦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直是家常茶便饭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未来远景多灿烂？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事在人为不虚玄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当前跃进是榜样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨上火箭往前赶。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}